OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLineker: BBC should have   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fspoken up on Russia 2018   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Football presenter Gary Lineker has    
OL,6, said he and the BBC should have spoken 
OL,7, out more about human rights issues     
OL,8, during the World Cup in Russia in 2018.
OL,10,FLineker, who is fronting BBC coverage  
OL,11,Fof this year's World Cup in Qatar,     
OL,12,Fsaid: "I think we were sportswashed    
OL,13,Ffour years ago when we were in Russia."
OL,15,FHe added: "I do look back four years   
OL,16,Fand feel slightly uncomfortable."      
OL,18,FThere were calls for Russia to be      
OL,19,Fstripped of the 2018 tournament after  
OL,20,Fit annexed Crimea in 2014.             
